HOW TO BUY $FOSSA

create a metamask wallet

Download Metamask or a wallet of your choice from the following list and create a wallet:
  • Coinbase Wallet – Best for Beginners
  • MetaMask – Best for Desktop
  • TrustWallet – Best for Mobile
We recommend you confirm you are on the correct website when clicking any links or doing anything related to cryptocurrency. Do not get scammed!

BUY ETHEREUM

In order to purchase $FOSSA, you must have ETH. To acquire ETH, you can purchase it from several centralized exchanges such as Coinbase, Binance and KuCoin. You must then send the ETH from the exchange to your wallet.

CONNECT TO UNISWAP

Go to Uniswap and connect your wallet of choice to the dApp. Paste the $FOSSA token address into the output currency if it is not already loaded.

The contract address for $FOSSA is 0xc1D9f4619c2516b25d67a10357fAD75f158AfA9B.
Any contract addresses other than this are fake and may be a scam/honeypot. Be careful.
